description: This is a list of entries in RNAcentral to be imported by ensembl. This list should be kept small enough to easily fit in memory and thus not all entries at once.

items.description: This is an entry in RNAcentral that is active (has at least 1 active xref)
items.title: RNAcentral Entry

___taxon_id.description: NCBI taxon id of the organism

___description.description: Human readable name of the sequence

___sequence.description: The sequence in uppercase with U's.

___xrefs.description: A list of cross references that other databases can use. These will only be the 'high quality' references from RNAcentral.

items.description: This represents a reference from this sequence to a different high quality database that RNAcentral can provide
items.title: RNAcentral Cross-reference

___database.description: Human readable name of the database this Xref comes from

___id.description: ID of this sequence in this database

___rnacentral_id.description: The specific specific URS of the sequence in RNAcentral

___rna_type.description: The INSDC type of the sequence

___md5.description: The MD5 hash of the sequence in lowercase
